com.tractrac.model.lib.api.spatial

Interface ICoordinate


  • public interface ICoordinate

    A raw coordinate.

    A coordinate may and may not have a z and m ordinate. If z and m is not valid, a value of Double.NaN must be returned

    Author:
    Jesper Grooss
